code: @Bean @ConditionalOnMissingBean(name = "couchbaseReactiveHealthIndicator") public ReactiveHealthIndicator couchbaseReactiveHealthIndicator(Map<String, Cluster> clusters) {     return createHealthIndicator(clusters). }
